        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'What\\'s wrong?', 3: '9', 4: 'Who\\'s Amberia?', 5: '10'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": 1004,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Just a name I never thought I\\'d hear again—Amberia...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": 1004,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'She is the sin borne by the Forest Guard...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 1004,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I originally planned on keeping you out of this, but seeing as the bionics mentioned her name, I think you should know who we\\'re up against.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Before the Punishing Virus, the ARU was also a prosperous metropolis.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Even at the start of the outbreak, it remained untouched just as life was before. There were no cases in the city.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Some people even had no idea what the virus was. Amidst our naivety, the ARU conducted one foolish experiment after another.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: '...The ARU applied the Construct tech given by the World Government to military science.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'They believed that the Punishing Virus would soon come to an end, and then the balance of the world would be shuffled anew.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'To get an edge in the new world, some of the decision makers and engineers decided to create a humanoid-hybrid Construct by the name of \"Amberia\".', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Not only a dreadnought on its own, Amberia can also command the bionic series that came with her conception.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 1005,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'The bionics serve Amberia?', 3: '19', 4: 'So who is Amberia...?', 5: '20'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": 1006,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Yeah. The bionics were developed as Amberia\\'s sub-units.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": 1006,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'We don\\'t know much about Amberia. Only that she was eighteen before she became a Construct.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 1006,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '8'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'The ARU wanted Amberia and the bionics to be their perfect weapons. But they never knew humanoid-hybrids could turn out to be such monsters.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'The bionics wielded immense power, but the ARU never thought that Amberia would go berserk upon her activation.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'The ARU became hell on earth in an instant. Amberia and her bionics ravaged the land, killing countless people in a sea of fire and brimstone.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 1007,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '14'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'To contain Amberia, the ARU dispatched an innumerable amount of ships and narwhals, like Derek. The sacrifices were countless...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 1008,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Did they win?', 4: 'Did Amberia die?'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Yes. Amberia was vaporized in a barrage of explosives, and we lost her signal. The battle was finally over.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'But the ARU also lost it all. Even before the ravages of the virus, this land was already in ruins because of Amberia.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Afterwards, all engineers involved in creating her were either executed or imprisoned for life. As for their family and closest friends...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'They were branded as sinners.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 5000,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'The Forest Guards...', 3: '29', 4: 'Are you the descendants of those engineers?', 5: '30'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": 1009,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Yes. They were later modified and labeled as traitors of the ARU—the Forest Guards.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": 1009,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Some yes—others no. Regardless, we are all seen as sinners.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 1009,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '4'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: '...But as I said, Amberia should\\'ve been killed long ago, but the bionics just mentioned her name.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 1010,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Could it be just a bug?', 3: '32', 4: 'Amberia must be alive.', 5: '34'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": 33,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'Whether it\\'s a bug or not, the number of bionics we\\'ve been seeing is already suspicious. There shouldn\\'t have been so many left after that battle.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": 35,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'It\\'s possible that Amberia is still alive.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": 35,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'That\\'s what I was thinking, Commandant.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'But that would mean we\\'ve been fighting the bionics under her control and mistook them for the \"Tide\" this whole time.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": 1,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": "AniZhuanchangBegin",
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Rosetta', 3: 'I can\\'t say for sure about the past tides, but this one... I think we should confirm this with the captain.', 4: '1'}"
    }
]